Six time Emmy nominated cartoon The Powerpuff Girls will be heading to South African shores for the first time ever. The crime-fighting trio, made up of Blossom, Bubbles and Buttercup, are set to perform at the Cartoon Network Live! show. If you're a fan, you can look out for the Powerpuff Girls in Cape Town from 26 June, and Johannesburg from 3 July as they join forces with other Cartoon Network characters at the Cartoon Network Live! show. Check out details for the show tour below: Cape Town: 26 June - 1 July Grand Arena, GrandWest Tickets: R245 - R365 Johannesburg: 3 July - 15 July Monetcasino Tickets: R175-390 Source: Supplied